This folder contains scripts to be used with Citrix NetScaler load balancer devices.

netscaler_bkup.py - This script will perform a full backup of a NetScaler device and copy the .tgz file via scp to a server.
                    It will append a date time stamp to the filename. It uses a commands.txt file to remove previously
                    created backup file on the NetScaler and creates a new backup file to be copied off to a server via scp.
